title: Fever fall to Lynx on buzzer-beater in WNBA Finals Game 3
text:
Published By: Indy Star: Sports - Today 
Maya Moore sank a 3-pointer as time expired, lifting the Minnesota Lynx over the Indiana Fever 80-77 Friday night and within one victory...
